{"tid":1607617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一日，國殤七十檄文。","createTime":"2019-10-01T01:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:46:08.000Z","uid":28609,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"427b0e0e9a6873a28c768f1cd8e2e37c3b03cefb","tid":1607617,"uid":28609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"國殤七十，十月一日，民憤焚城，所為何事？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一曰管治無能，吾城淪陷廿二載，政行混亂，朝令夕改，高官不仁，殘民以自肥，首長不義，害人以乞權。罪眾任行己意，肆作胡為，罔顧百姓之需，公帑錯配傾斜，只惠陸民，放棄港人。共匪得寸進尺，敢行送中惡法，圖斷香城百年之基，我城義民，焉能不反？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二曰警權專橫，革命百日，舉目所視，黑警鷹犬，視紀律若兒戲，棄良知如糞土，肆無忌憚，揮掍擎槍，濫行施暴，無顧人權。官警鄉黑，屢屢聯手，以公權濟私利，以暴拳向市民，卑侮公僕，敗法亂紀，爵賞由心，刑戮在口，所愛光五宗，所惡驅三族。無數衛士，白遭欺侮，茲等斷手亡眼，奪貞污節，毒打致死之事，吾等莫敢遺忘，未還新屋嶺之白，我城義民，焉能不反？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三曰殘害教本，匪類不識智，欲以國民教育之名，行集中洗腦之實。恃權凌人，簒改歷史，望持空廢文本，荼毒學子心智。幸我等青苗，心如冰鏡，智比天高，堅毅若寒中松柏，秉鴻火之志，燃亮己身，佇立在前，頂天立地，與惡相搏。百日以來，此情此景，歷歷在目，二百萬人，如心未冷，我城義民，焉能不反？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是故，共匪橫行，人災致禍，天理不能容，人神所共憤，吾城義士，爰舉義旗，以清妖孽，替天行道。鼓聲動而北風起，劍氣沖而港府平，喑嗚則山嶽崩頹，叱吒則風雲變色。以此制敵，何敵不摧？以此圖功，何功不克？一城之怨未消，廿載之恨何寄？還看今日之城中，竟是誰人敢擋之天下！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十月一日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賀佢老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(編按，因時所限，文句多有參考03年香港七一大遊行之「討董檄文」及唐代駱賓王《為徐敬業討武曌檄》，還望諸君見諒)"},{"pid":"d802c656ff2454de26d2ac7ade0882acf9742073","tid":1607617,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=36775100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=c3be7934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=45a589ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=c1953171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=3885a259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=86645391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"d519917270d9e1f865ad729e84eb6d762509583e","tid":1607617,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e65ae3276f6f7cb503e184afc84f002a2376ead","tid":1607617,"uid":6770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:01:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d74ad1a3a2a4d3392f6e08b6cb11c97de348264d","tid":1607617,"uid":28609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"153fe246df3d86a59893455a3f54cf5164b6b49e","tid":1607617,"uid":28609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"7f974f938851dbb42b6d8e98a1e4d9985876ca6d","tid":1607617,"uid":28609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"15f71c27c3c0e364162cf1d6a421b0ff2702c814","tid":1607617,"uid":28609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"01a45c11f58d91451a03c19bcb7e14734593ffc9","tid":1607617,"uid":28609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:04:28.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"739a25939c485bb7a0f5e06567145176a2123dd1","tid":1607617,"uid":28609,"like":0,"